355
00:26:36,460 --> 00:26:37,420
We'll be able

356
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,700
to watch the stars while enjoying the cool.

357
00:26:45,580 --> 00:26:46,100
What's wrong?

358
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:49,140
Nothing.

359
00:26:50,500 --> 00:26:52,620
I suddenly realized that

360
00:26:53,220 --> 00:26:55,540
