362
00:26:59,620 --> 00:27:00,060
Home?

363
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:03,260
Though we may not stay here for long every year,

364
00:27:03,460 --> 00:27:04,780
it's still our home.

365
00:28:26,180 --> 00:28:26,780
Xiaobai.

366
00:28:33,580 --> 00:28:35,340
I like to hear you say "our home".

367
00:28:45,580 --> 00:28:46,580
I've always liked it.

368
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:59,140
Greetings, Third Prince.

369
00:28:59,580 --> 00:29:00,100
Chong Lin.

370
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:02,540
What's the matter with His Majesty?

371
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:04,620
Why would he appoint Ye Qingti as his successor?

372
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:10,220
His Majesty felt that he related to

373
