00:29:12,700 --> 00:29:13,820
Your Highness, your concern is misplaced.

375
00:30:36,220 --> 00:30:37,260
That's a sign of something.

376
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:40,500
Chong Lin.

377
00:30:41,100 --> 00:30:42,540
Are you going to try to keep it from me?

378
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:44,260
