382
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:51,140
It's too much for me.

383
00:30:51,300 --> 00:30:52,220
You are in charge of things in the Tai Chen Palace.

384
00:30:52,340 --> 00:30:53,580
How could you not know anything?

385
00:30:54,100 --> 00:30:55,220
Even an ordinary man

386
00:30:55,380 --> 00:30:57,580
can't just die suddenly with no reason.

387
00:30:59,300 --> 00:30:59,860
Chong Lin.

388
00:31:00,460 --> 00:31:01,580
After all the twists and turns

389
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:02,620
Fengjiu and His Majesty have been through,

390
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:04,980
