391
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:06,860
If you know anything,

392
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:08,540
please tell her.

393
00:31:10,020 --> 00:31:10,500
Chong Lin.

394
00:31:11,980 --> 00:31:12,660
Tell her all about it.

395
00:31:19,140 --> 00:31:20,860
I'll begin with the big war

396
00:31:21,020 --> 00:31:22,380
thirty thousand years ago.

397
00:31:23,380 --> 00:31:25,060
Back then, the Demon King Miao Luo was a rebel

398
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:26,540
against His Majesty who dominated the universe.

399
00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:28,100
So she started killing recklessly,

400
00:31:28,500 --> 00:31:29,740
which triggered the war between the gods and the demons.

401
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:31,980
When His Majesty was sealing Miao Luo,

402
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:34,580
she left two wisps of Red Qi.

403
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:37,060
One turned into primordial spirit blood tear

404
00:31:37,980 --> 00:31:39,740
and was sealed in the Forbidden Land in the demons.

405
00:31:41,020 --> 00:31:42,100
While the baby born in

406
00:31:42,500 --> 00:31:43,500
the war between the gods and the demons

407
00:31:43,780 --> 00:31:47,020
was stained with the other Red Qi in her divine sense.

408
00:31:49,780 --> 00:31:52,940
The baby born in that war was....

409
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:55,140
...was me.

410
00:31:58,500 --> 00:31:58,980
But

411
00:31:59,260 --> 00:32:01,220
what does it have to do with His Majesty's end?

412
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:04,820
His Majesty found out about your relationship with Miao Luo

413
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:07,380
in the Dream of Aranya.

414
00:32:20,860 --> 00:32:22,100
Young punk.

415
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:24,580
You think you can seal me?

416
00:32:27,780 --> 00:32:28,420
Dong Hua.

417
00:32:29,340 --> 00:32:31,420
It's time for us to end this.

418
00:32:32,380 --> 00:32:32,860
Come out!

419
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:43,100
You finally show up.

420
00:33:11,820 --> 00:33:13,300
Since you want to end this,

421
00:33:14,180 --> 00:33:15,900
I'll put an end to it.

422
00:33:31,820 --> 00:33:33,860
His Majesty knew he couldn't suppress Miao Luo for long.

423
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:35,100
So for all these years,

424
00:33:35,700 --> 00:33:36,780
he had to reinforce the seal

425
00:33:36,900 --> 00:33:38,260
to prolong the time.

426
00:33:39,780 --> 00:33:40,660
However,

427
00:33:41,260 --> 00:33:42,140
Miao Luo got her power back

428
00:33:42,220 --> 00:33:43,940
way quicker than expected.

429
00:33:46,500 --> 00:33:47,780
Miao Luo was greatly weakened with her power

430
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:48,900
and sealed by His Majesty.

431
00:33:49,060 --> 00:33:50,540
How did she recover so quickly?

432
00:33:51,140 --> 00:33:52,340
Miao Luo worked her way out step by step.

433
00:33:53,300 --> 00:33:54,460
She first got Lingbi Stone.

434
00:33:54,860 --> 00:33:56,740
Then she got Red Qi back in Fengjiu's body

435
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,940
while the Dream of Aranya was being broken.

436
00:34:00,140 --> 00:34:01,820
Finally, she managed
to get back the demons' holy item, blood tear.

437
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:03,100
That's why she could break the seal.

438
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:04,740
At first,

439
00:34:05,340 --> 00:34:06,620
His Majesty and I didn't know about that.

440
00:34:07,980 --> 00:34:08,860
Before the wedding,

441
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:10,700
Ji Heng coerced His Majesty to meet her

442
00:34:10,700 --> 00:34:12,540
with her father's dragon scale.

443
00:34:13,340 --> 00:34:15,540
Ji Heng wanted to force His Majesty out of marrying you

444
00:34:15,660 --> 00:34:17,460
with dragon scale, which His Majesty couldn't stand.

445
00:34:18,220 --> 00:34:19,940
In the end, he transferred Ji Heng's Qiushui Cold Toxin

446
00:34:20,100 --> 00:34:22,060
all to himself,

447
00:34:22,740 --> 00:34:24,500
so that she could never leave the demons.

448
00:34:25,220 --> 00:34:28,700
But things went wrong with the demons right then.

449
00:34:31,740 --> 00:34:35,140
So His Majesty stayed at the demon clan

450
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:37,500
not for Ji Heng,

451
00:34:38,540 --> 00:34:39,660
but for Miao Luo.

452
00:34:41,900 --> 00:34:42,540
His Majesty has only loved you

453
00:34:42,740 --> 00:34:44,860
for the whole time.

454
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:46,780
Your Highness.

455
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:49,060
Do you know how to remove the Qiushui Cold Toxin quickly?

456
00:34:49,940 --> 00:34:50,900
The quickest approach is to

457
00:34:51,060 --> 00:34:53,660
transfer the toxin all to himself

458
00:34:53,980 --> 00:34:56,260
and then take medicine while cultivating.

459
00:34:56,940 --> 00:34:58,300
That's the approach His Majesty chose.

460
00:34:58,580 --> 00:35:00,220
He'd rather live with toxin

461
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:01,460
than let the demon princess

462
00:35:01,540 --> 00:35:03,460
bother you in any way.

463
00:35:05,300 --> 00:35:07,940
His Majesty went down to the mortal realm for misfortune

464
00:35:08,460 --> 00:35:10,980
because he spent too much cultivation

465
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:12,860
when sealing the Miaoyi Chasm.

466
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:15,980
You know how it went.

467
00:35:16,580 --> 00:35:17,900
His Majesty failed to get all his cultivation back

468
00:35:17,980 --> 00:35:19,380
till the end.

469
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:21,620
From the day he woke up,

470
00:35:21,820 --> 00:35:24,060
he's been preparing for

