528
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:03,700
What is it?

529
00:38:04,460 --> 00:38:05,500
Well, according to common rules,

530
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:08,340
your fates should be revised
because His Majesty asked the Fate Stone about it.

531
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,900
It's such a pity that

532
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:13,020
your hard-earned destiny with each other

533
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:14,820
