541
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:41,060
We were just not meant to be.

542
00:38:42,700 --> 00:38:43,700
Not meant to be.

543
00:38:44,620 --> 00:38:46,860
His Majesty was keeping his relationship with you

544
00:38:47,500 --> 00:38:48,740
